chainsaw
Class Chainsaw

java.lang.Object
  chainsaw.Chainsaw

public class Chainsaw
extends java.lang.Object

Class that models a Chainsaw. Stores all data for Chainsaw and provides update and query methods.

Version:
2.1, April 2008, (based on v2.0, February 2008)
Author:
Kevan Buckley and modified by Joshua Adam Woodyatt.
